      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a dedicated project or a donor for parts. The engine currently fails to hold a steady idle and requires a jump-start to turn over, while the transmission exhibits significant slipping when warm. The body shows heavy wear including several deep scratches and rust spots, and the interior will need a complete overhaul. Please expect to tow this vehicle as it is not currently reliable for road use.",
